  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP18\UI\Tutorial\EP18_Lesson_BusinessPerks_Slide1.png">2f7d0004:00000000:2c9bc574b6483827</T>
      <T n="text">0xEFC46DF1<!--As your Sim works hard to grow their Small Business, they're bound to learn some nifty tricks along the way! Every time the Small Business Renown <b><font color='#199C2C'>levels up</font></b>, your Sim will be rewarded with <b><font color='#199C2C'>Small Business Perk Points</font></b>.\n\nThese can be spent to unlock <b><font color='#199C2C'>Small Business Perks</font></b> in the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Small Business Perks Screen</font></b>, located in the Small Business panel.--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP18\UI\Tutorial\EP18_Lesson_BusinessPerks_Slide2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:2c9bc574b6483824</T>
      <T n="text">0x8B993FC9<!--Small Business Perks can change the way your Sim runs their Business! Some are <b><font color='#199C2C'>passive</font></b> and will be in effect once unlocked. You can turn some of them off via the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Ticket Kiosk, Business Sign</font></b> or the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Computer</font></b>. Others unlock <b><font color='#199C2C'>interactions</font></b> that your Sim can perform.\n\nSmall Business Perks are associated with <b><font color='#199C2C'>Dreamer</font></b>, <b><font color='#199C2C'>Schemer</font></b> or <b><font color='#199C2C'>Neutral</font></b> Small Business Alignments. When choosing the interactions that are linked to either Dreamer or Schemer Alignment, your Sim's Small Business Alignment will be affected each time.--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
